short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyze the time and space complexity of your code.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyzr is a Chrome extension designed to simplify your coding experience on platforms like LeetCode and GeeksforGeeks by providing instant insights into time and space complexity. With seamless integration, it automatically analyzes algorithms as you browse, offering clear, concise metrics to enhance your understanding and efficiency. Perfect for students, developers, and competitive programmers, Analyzr helps you write optimized code and ace coding interviews. Save time and improve your skills with this indispensable tool for any serious coder. Upgrade your coding toolkit today with Analyzr and gain a competitive edge.
